      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in great shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It has a little bit of character from normal use, but it's been well-cared for and drives beautifully! I'm super excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
