      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is sorted with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and tactile feedback these cars are known for. While the aesthetics show minor signs of use, the drivetrain is dialed in for performance driving. A purist-spec machine for the discerning driver.",
