    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2019 Lexus ES 350 is a pristine example of refined luxury and steadfast reliability. Finished in an elegant Eminent White Pearl, the exterior retains a deep luster, showing only the minor, expected road-wear of a well-loved daily driver, such as faint stone chips on the lower valence. The interior is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring Parchment leather-trimmed seats that remain supple and free of tears or heavy bolsters wear. Every technological feature, from the premium sound system to the intuitive navigation, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs with signature Lexus smoothness, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized centers. With a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires and responsive brakes, this sedan offers a quiet, composed ride that feels as solid today as it did on the showroom floor. Non-smoker owned and garage-kept, it is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 36500.0,
